 Mhlongo will host the awards taking place on 27 May in Sun City.After successfully hosting with Generations: The Legacy actress Thando Thabethe last year he is getting a new female co-host this year.He will host alongside award-winning comedienne Tume Morake. Our team is hard at work putting together a ceremony befitting the stature of the SAMAs, RiSA CEO Nhlanhla Sibisi expressed in a statement. We have every faith in Somizi and Tumi that they will add that extra zing to the proceedings and leave us entertained. 